When you're older and want to find me,

54
00:04:23,550 --> 00:04:24,610
just say, "Are you cold?"

55
00:04:24,610 --> 00:04:26,110
I'll let you wear my clothes,

56
00:04:26,110 --> 00:04:27,370
and I'll know it's you.

57
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,190
Boss?

58
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:34,790
Boss!

59
00:04:36,230 --> 00:04:37,270
I’m asking you.

60
00:04:37,950 --> 00:04:39,880
Why are you asking if they're cold?

61
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:42,990
"Are you cold?"...

62
00:04:44,230 --> 00:04:46,630
