63
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,650
Only he knows it.

64
00:04:49,670 --> 00:04:50,390
Sai'er.

65
00:04:51,110 --> 00:04:52,510
Her Highness will be asking for me

66
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,870
to serve her at her place.

67
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,510
Send these flyers out for me.

68
00:04:56,110 --> 00:04:58,350
Remember to go to places where there is

69
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:00,340
more human traffic, such as the inns,

70
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:01,740
theatres and teahouses.

71
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,140
And the martial club!

72
00:05:03,790 --> 00:05:05,250
That's where more men are.

73
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:06,960
