77
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:15,190
Remember to go to the martial club!

78
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:15,830
Okay.

79
00:05:33,310 --> 00:05:34,070
Linglong.

80
00:05:35,550 --> 00:05:36,550
Shuijing.

81
00:05:37,150 --> 00:05:37,870
Daimao.

82
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:40,040
Huanpei.

83
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:43,310
My lord.

84
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,050
You're back so soon?

85
00:05:46,370 --> 00:05:48,030
I'm back with one piece of good

86
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:49,090
and bad news each.

87
00:05:49,409 --> 00:05:51,340
Which one do you want to hear first?

88
00:05:53,530 --> 00:05:54,590
The bad news first.

89
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:55,820
General Nan has fled to

90
00:05:55,820 --> 00:05:56,680
the South.

91
00:05:56,909 --> 00:05:58,950
We don't know which state specifically.

92
00:05:58,950 --> 00:05:59,990
After Tumen collapsed,

93
00:05:59,990 --> 00:06:01,300
both Gongye and Moqi clans

94
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,100
were revived.

95
00:06:02,790 --> 00:06:04,310
Without anyone in charge of Heman,

96
00:06:04,310 --> 00:06:06,040
the people can't live in peace.

97
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:08,870
At this point,

98
00:06:09,230 --> 00:06:10,760
what good news can there be?

99
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:14,350
Before Nan Jifeng went missing,

100
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:16,080
he did leave some clues behind.

101
00:06:16,290 --> 00:06:17,430
He sent his old army buddies

102
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:18,690
to protect his parents

103
00:06:18,790 --> 00:06:19,870
and dismissed

104
00:06:19,870 --> 00:06:21,070
his family's servants and generals in advance.

105
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:22,730
It looks like he was prepared.

106
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:23,790
My lord.

107
00:06:24,270 --> 00:06:25,550
If Nan Jifeng had

108
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:27,450
predicted this would happen,

109
00:06:27,710 --> 00:06:28,830
why didn't he

110
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:29,960
tell you in advance?

111
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,780
I'm afraid it's because he couldn't.

112
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,930
The mastermind is in the capital,

113
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,110
so his messages and letters

114
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:37,909
can't enter the capital either.

115
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:41,240
There's something I forgot.

116
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,190
Someone has been asking about

117
00:06:42,190 --> 00:06:43,520
your marriage in Heman.

118
00:06:44,030 --> 00:06:45,890
They even drew Ms. Yan's portrait

119
00:06:45,990 --> 00:06:47,470
and sent it back to the capital.

120
00:06:47,470 --> 00:06:48,360
Don't worry, my lord.

121
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,420
I've already swapped the portraits.

122
00:06:57,710 --> 00:06:58,570
Who do you think

123
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,110
could be behind this?

124
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:06,150
This girl.

125
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,490
She's always up to something.

126
00:07:12,590 --> 00:07:13,230
Ruoqian.

127
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,110
What new products

128
00:07:14,110 --> 00:07:15,710
did Blossom Beauty release?

129
00:07:16,110 --> 00:07:16,940
Our new products

130
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:18,470
include hibiscus snow powder

131
00:07:18,470 --> 00:07:20,310
and orange osmanthus rouge.

132
00:07:36,990 --> 00:07:38,650
This bride is not Yan Nanxing.

133
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,940
How could this happen?

134
00:07:55,409 --> 00:07:55,930
Miss?

135
00:07:59,210 --> 00:08:00,140
It's really you.

136
00:08:01,710 --> 00:08:02,470
It's you.

137
00:08:03,110 --> 00:08:03,670
Miss,

138
00:08:03,909 --> 00:08:05,440
are you waiting for a guest?

139
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:10,910
Do you...

140
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,810
think I have a guest?

141
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:15,990
Your guest...

142
00:08:16,350 --> 00:08:17,410
didn't ask for you?

143
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:20,310
What?

144
00:08:20,740 --> 00:08:22,390
Do you come here often?

145
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,030
Yes, I do.

146
00:08:30,590 --> 00:08:32,050
Well, that's unexpected.

147
00:08:32,550 --> 00:08:33,580
Looks like...

148
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:35,950
you won't get the reward again tonight.

149
00:08:35,950 --> 00:08:36,430
So what?

150
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:39,000
Are you going to give me a red packet again?

151
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:40,659
Fine.

152
00:08:45,659 --> 00:08:46,720
Let me support you.

153
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:48,909
Well...

154
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,330
What do you want me to do?

155
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:53,650
If you don't want to sing or dance,

156
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:55,030
just chat with me.

157
00:08:55,630 --> 00:08:56,550
That's all?

158
00:08:57,260 --> 00:08:58,710
You don't have any customers, do you?

159
00:08:58,710 --> 00:08:59,460
Something's better

160
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:00,260
than nothing.

161
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,480
What are you doing here?

162
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,550
I'm chatting with this lady.

163
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:07,600
What are you talking about?

164
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,860
You shouldn't be here.

165
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:09,870
Don't offend her.

166
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:12,110
Why would I?

167
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,740
I have given her money.

168
00:09:14,070 --> 00:09:14,870
Are you crazy?

169
00:09:14,890 --> 00:09:16,290
She's an esteemed guest.

170
00:09:17,990 --> 00:09:19,710
Sorry, he didn't mean it.

171
00:09:20,910 --> 00:09:21,750
You may leave.

172
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,450
Say no more.

173
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,540
You're on your own.

174
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,960
So you're not a dancer.

175
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:39,430
Please pardon me.

176
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:41,920
You want me to pardon you

177
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:43,290
with a simple apology?

178
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:44,510
Then...

179
00:09:44,890 --> 00:09:46,250
how can you forgive me?

180
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:49,950
These

181
00:09:49,970 --> 00:09:50,830
are all for you.

182
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:58,030
I'll show my support for you.

183
00:09:58,310 --> 00:09:59,640
Show me a song and dance.

184
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:02,390
I can't sing or dance.

185
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,110
How about this?

186
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:05,570
Show me whatever you know.

187
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:12,350
May I borrow your handkerchief?

188
00:10:14,110 --> 00:10:15,270
What for?

189
00:10:36,190 --> 00:10:37,850
Here's a flower for you, Miss.

190
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:40,350
How did that come about?

191
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:43,270
I hope you'll be magnanimous

192
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:44,870
and forgive my mistake.

193
00:10:53,540 --> 00:10:54,390
Go back first.

194
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:03,930
Your Grace,

195
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:05,270
Commander Shang has something urgent

196
00:11:05,270 --> 00:11:06,150
and won't be able to come.

197
00:11:06,150 --> 00:11:07,950
He asks for your understanding.

198
00:11:08,590 --> 00:11:09,190
It's okay.

199
00:11:13,210 --> 00:11:14,260
How did he do that?

200
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:17,120
[Guangyu Hall]

201
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,860
His Majesty is here.

202
00:11:19,470 --> 00:11:20,190
Father.

203
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:21,950
What brings you here?

204
00:11:22,490 --> 00:11:23,870
Add a set of bowl and chopsticks now.

205
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:24,990
No need!

206
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:27,850
I'm so angry that I'm full.

207
00:11:28,210 --> 00:11:32,980
[Everlasting Glory]

208
00:11:34,630 --> 00:11:36,070
Exactly who on earth

209
00:11:36,310 --> 00:11:37,770
made my father this angry?

210
00:11:39,590 --> 00:11:40,350
Jiang Zhiyi.

211
00:11:40,990 --> 00:11:42,990
Let me make this clear today.

212
00:11:43,470 --> 00:11:45,470
The heir of Yuejiang's Residence

213
00:11:45,710 --> 00:11:47,790
shall not only bear the Jiang surname,

214
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:50,520
but he must also consider himself Jiang at heart.

215
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:51,320
Otherwise,

216
00:11:51,860 --> 00:11:53,060
this person will only

217
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:54,630
bring disaster to our family.

218
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:56,190
But Father, Xinbai...

219
00:11:56,830 --> 00:11:58,630
It's okay if I have no grandsons.

220
00:11:58,830 --> 00:12:00,910
I'll just nurture my granddaughter instead.

221
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:01,910
But just in case,

222
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:03,940
if there ever comes a day where my granddaughter

223
00:12:03,940 --> 00:12:05,340
is also unsatisfactory,

224
00:12:05,430 --> 00:12:06,910
I'd rather choose

225
00:12:06,930 --> 00:12:08,460
someone else in the family.

226
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:23,480
Mr. Pei, you have a peaceful family.

227
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,390
You have three daughters

228
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:26,940
who treat you well and dear.

229
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:29,070
But in my opinion,

230
00:12:29,630 --> 00:12:31,090
you still lack something.

231
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:35,640
What do I lack?

232
00:12:36,810 --> 00:12:38,010
You're lacking a son.

233
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:44,070
Am I...

234
00:12:45,110 --> 00:12:46,040
really lacking?

235
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:47,630
Yes, you are.

236
00:12:48,470 --> 00:12:51,000
Your three daughters have yet to get married.

237
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,820
May I propose a marriage

238
00:12:53,220 --> 00:12:54,100
for Xinbai?

239
00:13:00,190 --> 00:13:01,070
Your Highness.

240
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,790
You have both a son and daughter,

241
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:05,590
and that makes your family complete.

242
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:06,420
But I...

243
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:10,170
I have three dearest daughters too.

244
00:13:10,170 --> 00:13:11,210
I'm very content.

245
00:13:13,190 --> 00:13:14,190
There's a saying,

246
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:15,910
"A grown daughter cannot be kept.

247
00:13:15,910 --> 00:13:18,110
Otherwise, it will turn into trouble."

248
00:13:18,890 --> 00:13:20,230
Why not let the two young people

249
00:13:20,230 --> 00:13:21,070
meet first?

250
00:13:21,110 --> 00:13:22,950
Who knows, they might hit it off.

251
00:13:27,390 --> 00:13:28,070
Mr. Pei,

252
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:31,350
my family is very open.

253
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:34,300
I don't mind Xinbai marrying into your family.

254
00:13:39,430 --> 00:13:40,290
Your Highness.

255
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:41,580
Well...

256
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:43,550
There's no need for that.

257
00:13:45,390 --> 00:13:46,590
Xinbai...

258
00:13:46,950 --> 00:13:49,030
is just doing his job in his capacity.

259
00:13:49,690 --> 00:13:52,130
It's inevitable that he would offend others.

260
00:13:52,130 --> 00:13:53,900
Besides, with instigation of outsiders,

261
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:55,190
the animosity between

262
00:13:55,210 --> 00:13:56,340
Xinbai and his grandfather

263
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:57,580
is getting deeper.

264
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:01,170
I would also like to ask you to watch over Xinbai.

265
00:14:03,310 --> 00:14:04,080
On this,

266
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:06,470
you can rest assured, Your Highness.

267
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:08,330
Of course I'll watch over Xinbai.

268
00:14:08,750 --> 00:14:09,470
However,

269
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:11,710
we don't have to set up a marriage

270
00:14:11,710 --> 00:14:13,070
just because of this.

271
00:14:13,990 --> 00:14:16,110
Only by becoming a real family

272
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:17,870
can I be at ease.

273
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,430
But...

274
00:14:23,010 --> 00:14:23,760
Mr. Pei.

275
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,250
Alright.

276
00:14:27,070 --> 00:14:27,630
Okay.

277
00:14:29,390 --> 00:14:30,350
Then...

278
00:14:31,770 --> 00:14:33,020
As per your opinion,

279
00:14:35,910 --> 00:14:37,950
my third daughter, Yaoyao,

280
00:14:38,990 --> 00:14:39,910
is outgoing.

281
00:14:40,390 --> 00:14:41,510
And as far as I know,

282
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:42,990
she and Xinbai

283
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:44,670
have met before.

284
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:48,790
But first, let's make it clear.

285
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:50,650
It's just for the two young people

286
00:14:51,190 --> 00:14:52,250
to meet each other.

287
00:14:52,370 --> 00:14:54,500
If they don't think well of each other,

288
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:56,200
then as parents,

289
00:14:56,710 --> 00:14:58,440
let's not force it any further.

290
00:15:00,230 --> 00:15:01,240
Of course.

291
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:07,190
Nanxing.

292
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:09,510
What does she want now?

